@page "/"
@inject IHostEnvironment HostEnvironment
@inject TimeProvider Time

<PageTitle>Bocchi Home Server</PageTitle>

<article class="bocchi-shell">
    <header>
        <h1>Bocchi Home Server</h1>
        <p class="lede">个人主页与 Blog 的内网内容工作台。M1 仅交付骨架，后续里程碑将逐步点亮各模块。</p>
    </header>

    <section aria-labelledby="status-heading">
        <h2 id="status-heading">运行状态</h2>
        <dl>
            <dt>版本</dt>
            <dd>@ServerInfo.Version</dd>
            <dt>环境</dt>
            <dd>@HostEnvironment.EnvironmentName</dd>
            <dt>服务器时间</dt>
            <dd>@Time.GetUtcNow().ToString("u")</dd>
            <dt>健康检查</dt>
            <dd><a href="/healthz">/healthz</a></dd>
        </dl>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="roadmap-heading">
        <h2 id="roadmap-heading">里程碑</h2>
        <p>详见仓库内 <code>Docs/Milestones.md</code>。当前已完成 M0（架构基线）与 M1（解决方案骨架）。</p>
    </section>
</article>
